Invocation Name: top restaurants
des:
Life's too short to eat a bad meal! 

Find out the top restaurants in over 20 U.S. cities, including London and Montreal. 

Our picks come 100% from editors, not advertisers.

Use Top Restaurants skill to:
- Find Top Restaurants in all major U.S. cities across multiple price ranges.
- Your choice to list restaurants from either “most expensive” or “least expensive”
- Save the restaurants that sound good to your Alexa App by saying “Save”
- Supporting cities include: Atlanta, Austin, Boston, Charleston, Chicago, Dallas, Denver, Detroit, Houston, Las Vegas, London, Los Angeles, Miami, Montreal, Nashville, New Orleans, New York, Philadelphia, Portland, San Diego, San Francisco, Seattle, Minneapolis, Washington D.C.

To stay up-to-date with new skills for cooks and food-lovers, visit soulfood.ai
